解。<br />\n<br />\n而對於警方多次強調總部內有孕婦及長期病患者等被困至深夜更係感到困惑，既然警方認為一般文職同事可以在中午時間自行離開，為何這些有特殊需要的人士卻不可以呢？究竟是示威者還是警方不讓他們離開呢？<br />\n<br />\n事實擺在眼前，我希望警方及個別電視台不要再誤導市民。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/450867315005279/posts/2318572871568038?s=100001313257075&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F450867315005279%2Fposts%2F2318572871568038%3Fs%3D100001313257075%26sfns%3Dmo&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr1%2F1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=661511ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/450867315005279/posts/2318572871568038?s=100001313257075&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:05:45.000Z","msg":"好！"},{"pid":"6962af4d5ab714ff57f659b0e6dde306704fb2d0","tid":1253314,"uid":69719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:09:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31d89eb63d1994b45bab3a3d72817df8c847db06","tid":1253314,"uid":221192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:10:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e6f2b10716bd985dc8ae443628b23ef479999bc9","tid":1253314,"uid":219042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:12:01.000Z","msg":"誠信破產<br />\n香港既治安點可以交比尼班人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係賤種黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea58e8f1c0d22c4e55560a820b06239d12d5d43","tid":1253314,"uid":111006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:12:05.000Z","msg":"文職都睇唔撚過眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc38a42bbcfee7a509a76c6f75a5ff56f22d537","tid":1253314,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:12:29.000Z","msg":"香港差佬真係好撚無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794afe7dcc9b935e44b2969f1cf15c8940ac3037","tid":1253314,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019